import React, { useState } from 'react' import PropTypes from 'prop-types' export default function Navbar(props) { const textMode=()=>{ if (props.mode==='light'){ setTextMode('dark') } else{ setTextMode('light') } } return (
{props.title}
  • {props.home}
  • {props.elementAbout}
) } Navbar.propTypes = { title: PropTypes.string, elementAbout: PropTypes.string, home: PropTypes.string } Navbar.defaultProps = { title: 'TextUtils', elementAbout: "About", home: "Home" }
